ive marketing tactics, but with Rhode=E2=80=99s impending launch, it=E2=80=
=99s worth considering how their approach
differs, too. For Rhode, talent and visuals are only part of the strategy: =
A lot of the brand=E2=80=99s success comes down to <em>how </em>it messages=
 what it=E2=80=99s selling. Obviously, Sephora already carries several simi=
lar makeup and skincare lines=E2=80=94like Makeup by Mario, Rare Beauty, To=
wer 28, and Glow Recipe=E2=80=94but Rhode=E2=80=99s more creative terminolo=
