iscerning insiders I know praised Bieber=E2=80=99s ability to make
=E2=80=9Cpeptides=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Clip peptide treatments=E2=80=9D a <=
em>thing</em>, instead of just calling Rhode=E2=80=99s bestselling item a <=
em>lip gloss</em>, which is exactly what it is. (Also, the =E2=80=9Cpeptide=
=E2=80=9D terminology helps create a skincare-makeup throughline for custom=
ers, which is important since Rhode started as a skincare brand and still c=
